    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Model Risk Level 2 analysis with Medium model influence and High decision consequence. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
